About this item

  • All-terrain WheelsThe folding cart features four 74in all-terrain wheels built to handle hard sand, mud, grass and all kinds of complex ground. The premium wagon wheels are made of superior PVC with strong abrasion resistance, silent shock absorber, 360 Rotation, no drag marks and enhance the impact resistance of the whole caster. The front wheels are equipped with brakes, which locks both the wheels and direction simultaneously effectively to stop and prevent the garden carts from moving.
  • Heavy Duty Folding WagonOur beach wagon for sand is made of high-strength steel frame and durable 600D oxford fabric. The metal frame is a welded structure that is very sturdy and durable, and will not bend or deform. The surface of the metal frame is anti-oxidation and corrosion-resistant, and it will not fade and rust when used outdoors for a long time. The fabric material is made of 600D oxford fabric and PVC coating to waterproof and durability. BUPPLEE wagons will be with you for a long time.
  • Compact Folding DesignConsidering outdoor use and space-saving storage, we have adopted a compact design that is easy to fold, carry, and store, further reducing storage volume. The foldable wagon can be folded into a mini size for easy storage at home, garage, and car boot. You can fold and carry the utility cart with one hand in a few seconds. BUPPLEE folding wagon will help reduce your burden and make your life more convenient.
  • Extra Large CapacityThis collapsible foldable wagon equipped with high quality heavy duty metal frame and can load up to 400LBS of cargo. This sports wagon cart possesses deeper and larger storage space: 33.7" L x 20.5" W x 15.8" H. The roomy internal volume and surprise loading capacity are both increased by % than other wagons overall. Two mesh cup holders beverages safe and sound.
  • Must-have for Enjoying lifeIf you want a larger capacity, higher quality, and more convenient to carry station wagon, our beach buggy wagon can meet all your needs and is your best choice. You can easily tow a cart of groceries home from the store and equipment to the beach, fishing or camping. The grocery cart also is suitable for family outings, gardening, outdoor concerts and movies, and sporting events or anywhere you want, which can be a simple and portable way to transport tools.

  • How much can this wagon load?

    Our wagon can hold 25 cartons of water(500ml each, 16 bottles);it can also carry a weight of 300 pounds.

  • May I ask whether this wagon really works well on all terrains?

    The wheel is 4" wide with a diameter of 7". The contact area between the tire surface and the ground is larger, and the wheel can move smoothly on any ground. At the same time, PVC material makes the wheel more durable.

  • If I am a lady or an elderly person, will this wagon be suitable?

    Our wagon is simple to operate, providing great convenience to carry heavy household items over short distances, therefore it is suitable for children, adults, ladies, and elders in their daily use when going out.

  • How does this wagon make my life easier?

    Compared with traditional wagons, our product doesnt need assembly. It is collapsible and easy to carry. The handle can be adjusted according to your height, the anti-fall device allows you to bend less.

  • Is this wagon sturdy?

    This beach wagon is equipped with a high-quality heavy-duty metal frame and durable 600D Oxford fabric. The metal frame is a welded structure that is very sturdy and durable. The fabric materials have waterproofing and durability.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
